title: The Collected Works of Guy de Maupassant
description:
This Halcyon Classics ebook anthology contains Guy de Maupassant's complete 13-volume short story collection (180 stories) and four of his short novels (UNE VIE, BEL AMI, PIERRE AND JEAN, and YVETTE).

Maupassant (1850-1893) was a popular 19th-century French writer and is considered to be one of the fathers of the modern short story.
